title: 'You are amazing!' Six-month-old makes his mummy proud
text: 'Keep going, keep going monkey! Oh my goodness pull your abs in! Go, go! 'You are amazing! Keep going come on keep going pull that core in. Good job!' Motherly love: Dana quickly showers her tot with affection after he completes his taxing plank But Rowan isn't finished after his first 34-second plank. He immediately tries for a second plank position, but his little legs have trouble holding out. Nonetheless he's smothered with kisses by his adoring mother, who cooes that she's 'so proud' of him.
